Package: wrdc
Type: Package
Title: Solar radiation data from the WRDC archive
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Marieke","Dirksen",email = "marieke.dirksen@knmi.nl",role = c("aut","cre"))
Maintainer: Marieke Dirksen <marieke.dirksen@knmi.nl>
Description: The solar radiation network is stored in the WRDC archive. The data is available since 1964. The functions in this package are build to download station data and meta data for Europe. Each country, station and year of data has its own html page. 
